{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 41,
  "title": "第四十一章（聞道）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "上士聞道，堇而行之。中士聞道，若存若亡。下士聞道，大笑之。弗笑，不足以為道。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以，建言有之曰：明道如費。進道如退。夷道如纇。上德如浴。大白如辱。廣德如不足。建德如偷。質真如渝。大方无隅。大器免成。大音希聲。天象无形。道殷无名。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯道，善始且善成。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 38,
          "end": 38
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上士聞道，自勤苦竭力而行之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 11,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "中士聞道，治身以長存，治國以太平，欣然而存之，退見財色榮譽，惑於情欲，而覆亡之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 22,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "下士貪狠多欲，見道柔弱，謂之恐懼。見道質樸，謂之鄙陋。故大笑之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 38,
          "end": 38
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不為下士所笑，不足以名為道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "建，設也。設言以有道，當如下句。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "明道之人，若闇昧無所見。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "進取道者，若退不及。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夷，平也。大道之人不自別殊，若多比類也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上德之人若深谷，不恥垢濁也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大潔白之人若汙辱，不自彰顯。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "德行廣大之人，若愚頑不足也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "建設道德之人，若可偷引使空虛也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "質樸之人，若五色有渝淺不明也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 69,
          "end": 70
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大方正之人，無委屈廉隅。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大器之人，若九鼎瑚璉，不可卒成也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 81,
          "end": 82
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大音猶雷霆待時而動，喻當愛氣希言也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大法象之人，質樸無形容。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道潛隱，使人無能指名也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "成，就也。言道善稟貸人精氣，且成就之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 38,
          "end": 38
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "有志也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "建，猶立也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "光而不耀。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "後其身而身先，外其身而身存。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "纇，㘨也。大夷之道，因物之性，不執平以割物，其平不見，乃更反若纇㘨也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不德其德，無所懷也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "知其白，守其黑，大白然後乃得。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "廣德不盈，廓然無形，不可滿也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "偷，匹也。建德者，因物自然，不立不施，故若偷匹。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "質真者，不矜其真，故渝。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 69,
          "end": 70
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "方而不割，故無隅也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大器成天下不持全別，故必晚成也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 81,
          "end": 82
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聽之不聞名曰希，不可得聞之音也。有聲則有分，有分則不宮而商矣，分則不能統眾，故有聲者非大音也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 75,
          "end": 75
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "有形則有分，有分者不溫則炎，不炎則寒。故象而形者，非大象。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "凡此諸善，皆是道之所成也。在象則為大象，而大象無形。在音則為大音，而大音希聲。物以之成而不見其成形，故隱而無名也。貸之非唯供其乏而已，一貸之則足以永終其德，故曰善貸也。成之不如機匠之裁，無物而不濟其形，故曰善成。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
